<h1 id="science-communication">Science communication</h1>

<p>I have participated in science communications events like The Jepson Herbarium Bryophyte Workshop (2019), Expand your Horizons (2018), Cal-Academy Nightlife stands (2019) and La Feria de las Ciencias (2016). I also co-designed and taught the class “Phylogenetic classification of plants” for highscool instructors with my collaborator Ana-Isabel Pérez-Mausan.</p>

